  "title": "Head of Legal (Marine Industry, Central Region)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead the legal team according to management directives and business needs.</li>\n  <li>Provide legal advice on matters related to commodity trading, overseas project development, and corporate mergers &amp; acquisitions.</li>\n  <li>Draft, review, and negotiate contracts and legal documents to manage legal risks.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with external law firms and coordinate domestic and international legal matters.</li>\n  <li>Support management with other legal and compliance-related tasks as assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor’s degree or higher in Law.</li>\n  <li>At least 7 years of relevant legal experience; prior exposure to corporate legal work or law firms is an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of corporate and contract law, as well as international trade regulations; experience in M&amp;A and legal matters related to engineering projects is a plus.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with the legal and regulatory environment in Southeast Asia is preferred.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>______________________________________________________</strong></p>\n<p><strong>HOW TO APPLY :</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Interested candidates, please submit your resume by clicking on “Quick Apply” or contact win@hkmsvs.com for more details.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Please provide following information in the resume for immediate processing</strong></p>\n<p><strong>1) Reasons for leaving current and/or last employment</strong></p>\n<p><strong>2) Last drawn and/or current salary</strong></p>\n<p><strong>3) Expected salary</strong></p>\n<p><strong>4) Date of availability and/or Notice Period</strong></p>\n<p><strong>All applications will be treated in strictest confidence and only shortlisted candidates will be notified</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Wee Wai Dan</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EA License No : 03C5391</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EA Reg No : R22109628</strong></p>",
